                                        2701,
                                        2167,
                                        3224
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "In Section 2, we define the total Segre class of a cone and introduce a generalized version of double point formula. This formula allows us to compute the total Segre class "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        310,
                                        2701,
