                                        2167,
                                        3224
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " in order to determine the degree of the 3- secant variety. However, the singularity of the 2- secant variety may impede this computation. To overcome this issue, we introduce the notion of higher very ampleness of a line bundle "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
